{"tid":256012,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"【韓星】27歲《繼承者們》金宇彬患鼻咽癌","createTime":"2017-05-24T08:22:38.000Z","updateTime":"2017-05-25T14:59:15.000Z","uid":42188,"like":10,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"441a60cf9e947db2070a3c58d558ebd0e1bd9796","tid":256012,"uid":42188,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-24T08:22:38.000Z","msg":"韓劇《繼承者們》27歲男星金宇彬，自上月先後現身泰國見面會及現身2018年平昌冬季殘奧會被委任宣傳大使儀式後，一直未有公開露面。<br />\n<br />\n其事務所今日公開金宇彬患鼻咽癌消息，表示：「因考慮到大家會擔心金宇彬的狀態，我們以這種方式正式發佈聲明。近期金宇彬感到身體不適，隨後到醫院檢查，診斷結果是鼻咽癌。慶幸發現尚早，已進行藥物治療及放射治療。近期會專注於接受治療，盡快以健康的狀態見大家。」<br />\n<img src=\"http://static.apple.nextmedia.com/images/e-paper/20170524/large/1495607131_d223.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstatic.apple.nextmedia.com%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20170524%2Flarge%2F1495607131_d223.jpg&h=e63f49f0&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6e04e72eb48d5cb1da7419f2aa5e6a41635395dd","tid":256012,"uid":42586,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-24T08:25:18.000Z","msg":"邊個嚟 咁樣衰<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"885de2234911bfdee7852dc4d139bcf9f1b88fe4","tid":256012,"uid":54190,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-24T08:26:55.000Z","msg":"積下口德啦"},{"pid":"cf99f9183d97b174c22ab16596ebe1c0ce158915","tid":256012,"uid":42188,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-24T08:30:12.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>積下口德啦</blockquote><br />\n希望佢早日康復！好返之後唔好再復發！<br />\n<br />\n口德+100"},{"pid":"25497017fd43c43227146a60ac9d54dc33ca3b95","tid":256012,"uid":37005,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-24T08:53:02.000Z","ms